org.apache.drill.common.expression.parser

Interface ExprParserListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExprParserBaseListener

    public interface ExprParserListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by ExprParser.
